ly modern Denmark and the Holy Roman Empire. Empresses and queens, but also mistresses and favourites are discussed, including considerations of their spheres of influence, their financial strategies and means, and their successes and failures.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 02. Mrz 2022) 4aHistory. 7aHISTORY / Renaissance.2bisacsh  aEconomy of Courts.  aFinancial Power.  aGender History.  aPremodern Rule.  aRoyal Studies.1 aBackerra, Charlotte, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aLudwig-Ockenfels, Cathérine, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aSarti, Cathleen, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aSarti, Cathleen, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aSeah, Michele, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aTompkins, Laura, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aWoodacre, Elena, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aWright, Katia, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertAmsterdam University Press Complete eBook-Package 2020z978311068955608iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Plus PP Package 2020 Part 2z978311069629508iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2020 Englishz978311070471608iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2020z9783110704518oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE History 2020 Englishz978311070473008iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE History 2020z9783110704525oZDB-23-DEG40uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/9781641892735zCo-access DOI >> click Walter de Gruyter40uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9